Normal condition :
=>-------------------------------------------------------------------=>
Conveyor Flow Direction =>                                     
                   |-----------------|    
                   |     Scanner     |  
                   |         y+      |   
    .....          |      ..|..      |          .....            .....
    .   .          |      . |___ x+  |          .   .            .   .
    .....          |      .....      |          .....            .....
                   |                 |       
                   |                 |  
                   |-----------------|        
Conveyor Encoder(+) into RTC MoF X(+) Encoder           
=>------------------------------------------------------------------=>

If scan head rotated 90 angle :
=>-------------------------------------------------------------------=>
                   Conveyor Flow Direction =>                                           
                   |-----------------|    
                   |(Rotated) Scanner|  
                   |        x+       |   
    .....          |      ..|..      |          .....            .....
    .   .          |  y+ ___| .      |          .   .            .   .
    .....          |      .....      |          .....            .....
                   |                 |       
                   |                 |  
                   |-----------------|   
Conveyor Encoder(+) into RTC MoF X(+) Encoder
Z angle to -90° with PrimaryHeadBaseOffset like as :

var head2nd = rtc as IRtc2ndHead;
var offset = new SpiralLab.Sirius2.Mathematics.Offset(0, 0, -90);
head2nd.PrimaryHeadBaseOffset = offset;
=>------------------------------------------------------------------=>

